AN ACT
To repeal sections 43.656, 56.265, 67.2540, 168.071, 190.142, 210.1080, 210.1505, 211.326,
315.005, 324.012, 324.035, 329.050, 337.618, 339.100, 542.301, 566.010, 566.147,
566.148, 566.149, 566.150, 566.155, 566.211, 566.218, 567.030, 573.010, 573.023,
573.025, 573.035, 573.037, 573.038, 573.050, 573.052, 573.110, 573.112, 573.215,
589.042, 589.400, 589.414, 590.050, 595.045, 610.131, 650.120, and 660.520, RSMo,
and to enact in lieu thereof forty-nine new sections relating to the protection of
children and vulnerable persons, with penalty provisions.
Be it enacted by the General Assembly of the state of Missouri, as follows:
Section A. Sections 43.656, 56.265, 67.2540, 168.071, 190.142, 210.1080, 210.1505,
